data.description: Discover the best deal in Westland with this adorable ranch home boasting updates galore! New vinyl siding and windows installed in 2023, ensuring both style and energy efficiency. New carpet throughout enhances the cozy atmosphere, while newer features including the furnace, hot water tank, A/C unit, and electrical/plumbing systems provide peace of mind. The carport has been thoughtfully converted into a spacious family room, complete with a gas heater for additional comfort. This versatile space could easily function as a third bedroom, perfect for accommodating guests or creating a home office. Whether you're looking for a place to entertain or relax, this home offers it all. Don't miss your chance to make this charming property yours!
